sequenceDiagram
    participant M as 主 Agent
    participant TT as task_tool
    participant SE as SubagentExecutor
    participant SA as 子 Agent(隔离线程)
    participant SS as StreamBridge

    M->>TT: task(description, subagent_type, prompt)
    TT->>TT: 解析配置<br/>模型/skills/timeout
    TT->>SE: submit_async(task)
    SE->>SE: 调度线程池分配
    SE->>SA: 在隔离事件循环中启动
    SA->>SS: 流式进度更新
    TT->>SS: 轮询进度(每5秒)
    SS-->>TT: 增量文本
    TT-->>M: Command(update)
    SA-->>SE: 完成/失败/超时
    SE->>SE: try_set_terminal()
    TT->>SE: 获取最终结果
    TT-->>M: 结果 + token_usage
